She might be celebrating her 75th birthday today
but an overjoyed Queen Margrethe of Denmark looked far younger as she waved to excited crowds from the balcony at the Amalienborg Palace
The Danish monarch was joined for the balcony appearance by her son and heir
Waiting below was an enormous flag-waving crowd who went into raptures as the royals appeared
